he LAPORTE] Voici un résumé de mes certifications. Pour la liste complète, merci de vous référer au transcript Microsoft\r\n?	MCT (?)\r\n?	MVP SQL Server (Profil MVP)\r\n?	Microsoft Certified Master – SQL Server 2008 (annonce) (?)\r\n?	MCITP Database Administrator (2005, 2008) (?)\r\n?	MCITP Database Developer (2008)\r\n?	MCITP Enterprise Administrator ( 2008)\r\n?	MCITP Server Administrator (2008)\r\n?	MCDBA (7.0, 2000) (?)\r\n?	MCSE (NT4 , 2000, 2003) (?)\r\n?	MCSA (?)\r\n?	MCSD (?)\r\n?	MCAD (?)\r\n\r\n      \r\n- Vos domaines d’intervention \r\n[Christophe LAPORTE] SQL Server, Cluster Windows, Virtualisation, Optimisation, Tolérance de panne\r\n\r\n Consultant SQL Server\r\nHyper v\r\nPrise de contact by KD le 19.10.11\r\nMicrosoft Windows Server 2008\r\nMicrosoft SQL Server 2008\r\nMicrosoft Exchange Server 2010\r\nMicrosoft Hyper-V\r\nMicrosoft System Center Virtual Machine Manager (SCVMM)\r\nMicrosoft Failover Cluster (MSCS)\r\nMicrosoft MSMQ\r\nMicrosoft IIS\r\nMicrosoft Office Sharepoint Server (MOSS)\r\nMicrosoft Windows Sharepoint Services (WSS)\r\nMicrosoft Forefront Server TMG (ISA Server)\r\nConsultant indépendant – Formateur certifié Microsoft\r\nExpert Microsoft SQL Server certifié\r\nSpécialiste environnement serveur Microsoft\r\nHaute disponibilité, tolérance de panne, virtualisation','contacté','christophe',50,'','',900);
